quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  97,1,We certainly sent it(Quran) down during the night of Al Qadr
  97,2,And what will make you realize what the night of Al Qadr is
  97,3,The night of Al Qadr is better than a thousand months
  97,4,The angels and the spirit come down during this night by the permission of their Lord with (a programme for) every affair
  97,5,Peace! it is till the appearance of dawn